
👽 test linux/amd64

[EXPERIMENTAL]

Install one or more CLI binaries using metadata from the registry.

The tool(s) should be specified in the format: owner/repo@version

Examples: atmos toolchain install hashicorp/terraform@1.5.0
mailto:hashicorp/terraform@1.5.0 atmos toolchain install opentofu@1.6.0 mailto:opentofu@1.6.0 tflint@0.50.0 mailto:tflint@0.50.0 kubectl@1.29.0 mailto:kubectl@1.29.0

USAGE


    $ atmos toolchain install [tool...] [flags]


EXAMPLES


    - Install all the tools added in .tool-versions

     $ atmos toolchain install


    - Install a specific version of a tool

     $ atmos toolchain install <tool>@<version>


FLAGS

      --default    Set as default version in .tool-versions

  -h, --help       help for install

      --reinstall  Reinstall even if already installed



Use --help=usage for examples or --help=all for all flags and full help.
